# The [[chief]] [[public]] [[representative]] of a [[nation]] having [[duties]], [[privilege]]s and [[responsibilities]] varying greatly depending on the [[constitution]]al rules; a [[monarch]] in a [[monarchy]], and often styled [[president]] in a [[republic]], but variations such as collegiality exist.

